name: The Brainchild/The Case of the Stolen Powers

deck: Electro is back with a vengeance!
description: Max Dillon is fully charged with about 30,000 volts of electricity in his body, with an addition of payback. He is out to finally get in touch with his love, a student of ESU named Sally. He will have to make her pure electricity to do that, but it's gonna be risky. What are you waiting for Spidey? Go get him!
name: When Sparks Fly

deck: What is happening to Spidey's world?
description:
Silver Sable has escaped from prison, with the help of Pterodax and has teamed-up with the vicious killer named Kraven the Hunter. Meanwhile, Spider-Man has met a couple of telepathic twins. They are the Gaines Twins. Roland is the brother and Roxanne is the sister. Soon after, evidence are surfacing that he is in a dream world. Is this real or is this just fantasy? With MJ dead, Spidey must escape this nightmare, before it's too late.

Note: Stan Lee is here by the name of Frank Elson.
name: Mind Games: Part One

description:
Here we go, true believers! This is the finale everyone's been waiting for. MJ is alive and it's only a matter of time for Spider-Man to fight one last time. The Gaines Twins have been behind his nightmare this whole time. they are making him kill Kraven as revenge for what he has done to the twins' parents. After hurting his crush, Indy, the entire Manhattan is out to make sure Spider-man is no more. Will Spider-Man survive or will Peter end him forever?

Note 1: This is marked as the series finale.

Note 2: Stan Lee returns again as Frank Elson.
name: Mind Games: Part Two

description: Part 1 of 2. Recruited soldiers escort Army intelligence to investigate Cobra's facilities and are surprised by what they find.
name: The Descent: Part 1

description: Conclusion. The Joes track a Cobra Bio-Viper while fleeing the military to evade punishment for a crime they did not commit.
name: The Descent: Part 2

description: Scrap-Iron kidnaps Tunnel Rat and uses him to test a weaponized exo-suit. Roadblock attempts a rescue by allowing himself to be kidnapped as well.
name: Rage

description: The Joes go on a mission to stop Zartan and his motorcycle gang from terrorizing a small town.
name: Dreadnocks Rising

description: The Joes stop the Baroness' mercenary from completing his planned assassination.
name: The Package

description: Part 1 of 2. The Joes train with Snake Eyes at his dojo and learn about his connection to Storm Shadow.
name: Return of the Arashikage, Part 1

description: Conclusion. The Joe team regroup after an ambush from Storm Shadow and must come up with a plan to rescue Jinx, who has been kidnapped.
name: Return of the Arashikage, Part 2

description: Duke is arrested while buying parts for the Coyote, and the Joes have to break him out of jail before others can find him.
name: Busted

description: The Joes penetrate a Cobra facility where an exo-armor weapon is being developed.
name: The Enemy of My Enemy

description: The Joes try to destroy a bio-viper facility, but are hindered by Firefly, a saboteur for Cobra.
name: Fire Fight

description: Part 1 of 2. Duke protects his family, who have been targeted by Cobra, while the team sneaks into Cobra's Christmas party.
name: Homecoming, Part 1

description: Conclusion. Baroness tries to hijack the Joes as they're being transported by Flint and Lady Jaye, so she can gain control of the secrets stored on Cobra's drive.
name: Homecoming, Part 2

description: Tomax and Xamot entrance the Joes and hold them in a commune.
name: Brothers of Light

description: Lady Jaye and Flint use Zartan to track the Joes. Meanwhile, the Baroness tries to sneak a camouflage suit to Cobra.
name: Knockoffs

description: The prototype Shadow-Vipers and Storm Shadow follow the Joes to Canada, where they are hiding out with Snow Job.
name: White Out

description: A sea captain helps the Joes transport a bio-viper canister taken from Cobra's lab, but things go wrong on the journey.
name: Shipwrecked

description: In Scotland, the Joes become trapped in Destro's castle while on a mission investigating a Cobra weapon.
name: Castle Destro

description: The Joes uncover a mind-control scheme at the baroness's château.
name: Union of the Snake

description: The Joes uncover a deadly virus while searching for a missing scientist and learn of Cobra's plan to profit from the sale of its antidote.
name: The Anaconda Strain

description: Cobra's medical facility is raided by the Joes, who are searching for Patient X.
name: Prodigal

description: The Joes head to New York to find a missing kid. While investigating, they encounter a Sewer Viper being pursued by a Mindbender.
name: The Anomaly

description: A Cobra commander is attacked by a ninja and forced to escape to his secure facility. Meanwhile, Snake Eyes and Scarlett sneak into the commander's facility.
name: Cutting Edge

description: Flint gets help from Heavy Duty to capture Roadblock. Meanwhile, Major Budd seeks revenge against the Joes.
name: Cousins

description: A series of earthquakes alerts the Joes to a network of tunnels Cobra is constructing to link its strongholds around the country.
name: Going Underground

description: Part 1 of 2. Cobra plans to increase its power by deploying the MASS device, but Scarlett plays a key role in its operation.
name: Revelations: Part 1

description: Conclusion. The Joes attack Cobra to stop the use of a dangerous device, expose its owners and clear the team's name.
name: Revelations: Part 2

deck: What happened to Agent Coulson when he "died"? Why is Tahiti a magical place? There will be some answers here.
description: Coulson uncovers vital information about the mystery of his death, but, with Centipede out for blood, this knowledge may come at the cost of one of the team on MARVEL'S AGENTS OF S.H.I.E.L.D.
name: The Magical Place
